<HEAD>Girl, 11, Charged with Selling Crack</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A foul-mouthed 11-year-old girl carrying a
beeper was arrested trying to sell crack, police said.
   ``As soon as she opened her mouth ... she called us every name
in the book,'' said Port Authority Police Officer William Smith.
   The girl ``looked like any 11-year-old girl, baby-faced, wearing
