Boston 16 fair; Buffalo 16; Charleston, S.C. 33 fair; Chattanooga
34 cloudy; Cincinnati 17 snow; Cleveland 6 cloudy; Detroit 1 fair;
Hatteras 31 fair; Jacksonville 35 fair; Key West 64 partly cloudy;
Knoxville 30 cloudy; Macon 29 fair; Miami 57 partly cloudy; New
York 26 fair; Philadelphia 19 fair; Pittsburgh 8 partly cloudy;
Portland, Maine 0 fair; Richmond 23 foggy; Tampa 44 partly cloudy;
Washington, D.C. 24 foggy.
   _CENTRAL: Birmingham 46 cloudy; Bismarck 20 fair; Chicago 2
cloudy; Denver 14 snow; Des Moines 11 fair; Fort Worth 32;
Indianapolis 10 snow; Kansas City 11 fair; Little Rock 39 partly
cloudy; Louisville 23 snow; Memphis 46 fair; Nashville 41 cloudy;
New Orleans 52 partly cloudy; North Platte 18 fair; Oklahoma City
20 windy; Omaha 12 windy; Rapid City 21 fair; St. Louis 6 snow;
