included: Michael Urquhart, president of the American Federation of
Government Employees Local 12; David Schlein, the AFGE national
vice president for the Washington metro area; Mark Simon, president
of the Montgomery County Education Association; and Paul Pinsky, a
member of the Maryland House of Delegates and former president of
the Prince George's County Educators' Association.
