   Lowery is a United Methodist minister who heads the Southern
Christian Leadership Conference.
   The prize, sponsored by the King Center, will be presented at
Atlanta's Ebenezer Baptist Church, where King preached, on Jan 15,
the national holiday in memory of King. The prize includes a cash
stipend of $1,000.
