<HEAD>Actress Gives Birth to Seven-Pound Boy</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Actress Brigitte Nielsen and former football
star Mark Gastineau are the parents of a boy.
   Marcus Gastineau was born at 2 a.m. Friday in an undisclosed
Scottsdale, Ariz., hospital, said the couple's publicist Joel
Brokaw. ``Mother and baby are doing well.''
   The 26-year-old actress, who co-starred in the movies ``Red
