Sylvester Stallone in the films ``Cobra'' and ``Rocky IV.''
   Miss Nielsen lives in Arizona with Gastineau, who is awaiting a
final divorce decree from wife Lisa. Gastineau, a former All-Pro
defensive end who was the key to the New York Jets' ``sack
exchange,'' quit football during the 1988 season.
